{
  "texts": [
    "This fused representation is then fed into a multi-layer neural network, facilitating joint learning across modalities.",
    "In this work, we employed the pre-trained OpenAI GPT-4V model [36] for image understanding and reasoning.As shown in Fig. 1 and explained in the system architecture section, the multi-modal LLM accepts a text prompt and an image of the labeled blood pools.",
    "The prompt outlines essential details about blood pools, including the presence of clots, and signs of active bleeding.",
    "Each of these aspects is crucial in deciding the urgency of suctioning blood pools during medical procedures.",
    "Size indicates the amount of blood, while clots indicate coagulation and cessation of blood flow."
  ]
}